headline: Q4 Rundown: Spectrum Brands (NYSE:SPB) Vs Other Household Products Stocks
summary: The end of an earnings season can be a great time to discover new stocks and assess how companies are handling the current business environment. Let’s take a look at how Spectrum Brands (NYSE:SPB) and the rest of the household products stocks fared in Q4.
